cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.SY

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics): The paper focuses on training predictive policies for skilled object grasping and ball throwing on a PR2 robot, indicating a robotics application.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper proposes a deep neural network policy architecture and uses reinforcement learning for training, indicating a machine learning approach.
- cs.CV (Computer Vision): The perception super-layer of the proposed architecture is trained on visual data, indicating a computer vision component.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper proposes a framework for training predictive policies using deep learning and reinforcement learning, indicating an AI focus.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper involves training policies for controlling a robot, indicating a systems and control component.
